						<p>Replies: 15</p>
						<p>Hello!<br />
I am using the Cloudflare plugin with Autoptimize. I have tried all the possible solutions to speed up my website but the mobile page speed result is still low.<br />
I am thinking of adding one more cache plugin called W3 Total Cache.<br />
